# Emoji Preservation

**Never change, remove, or replace emojis** when editing code, HTML, labels, buttons, or UI text.

- Keep existing emojis exactly as they are (e.g., 🔄, 🌙, ❤️, 🔒, 📋, 🛠️, etc.)
- Do not substitute emojis with other emojis
- Do not replace emojis with text or icons
- When adding new UI elements, emojis may be used if consistent with existing style
